<div class="notice">
    <h3>Important Notice</h3>
    <p>The College maintains a policy of non-interference in Skyrim's political conflicts. All students and staff are expected to remain neutral in the Civil War. Unauthorized use of magic for military purposes is grounds for immediate expulsion.</p>
